  "title": "DRIVER",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Class 4 Driver (Night Shift)</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>1. Drive and operate Class 4 vehicles to transport goods safely and efficiently.</p><p>2. Perform loading and unloading of goods independently (requires physical strength and stamina).</p><p>3. Ensure proper handling and secure transportation of goods.</p><p>4. Conduct vehicle inspections and basic maintenance to ensure roadworthiness.</p><p>5. Follow assigned delivery schedules and routes, ensuring timely completion of tasks.</p><p>6. Maintain accurate records of deliveries and follow company protocols.</p><p>7. Adhere to traffic regulations, workplace safety guidelines, and company policies.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>1. Possess a valid Class 4 driving license in Singapore.</p><p>2. Physically fit and capable of performing manual loading and unloading.</p><p>3. Comfortable with night shift work (including extended hours if required).</p><p>4. At least 1 year of experience as a heavy vehicle driver is preferred.</p><p>5. Ability to navigate routes using GPS and maintain delivery timelines.</p><p>6. Basic communication skills in English.</p><p>7. A responsible and safety-conscious attitude.</p><p>Working Hours:</p><p>· Night Shift: 6 working days per week (need to work on PH and weekend also)</p><p>主要职责：</p><p>1. 驾驶和操作Class 4车辆，安全高效地运输货物。</p><p>2. 独立完成货物的装卸工作（需要一定的体力和耐力）。</p><p>3. 确保货物妥善处理并安全运输。</p><p>4. 进行车辆检查及基本保养，确保车辆状况良好。</p><p>5. 遵循分配的送货时间表和路线，确保准时完成任务。</p><p>6. 维护送货记录，遵守公司规定和流程。</p><p>7. 严格遵守交通规则、工作安全准则和公司政策。</p><p>职位要求：</p><p>1. 持有新加坡有效的Class 4驾驶执照。</p><p>2. 身体健康，能够独立进行装卸工作。</p><p>3. 能接受夜班工作（包括必要时的延长工作时间）。</p><p>4. 拥有至少1年重型车辆驾驶经验者优先。</p><p>5. 熟练使用GPS导航，能够按时完成送货任务。</p><p>6. 具备基本的英语沟通能力。</p><p>7. 责任心强，重视安全。</p><p>工作时间：</p><p>· 夜班时间：每周工作6天， 需要在PH还有周末工作</p><p>We thank you for your interest and we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. All resumes received will be used for recruitment purposes only.</p><p>EA License ID: 18C9520</p><p>EA Registration ID: R1765753</p>",
